Since it is not clear if an email address is required or not, I will provide two possible JSONs:

If an email address is required:
{"name": "git_transfer_repo_ownership", "parameters": {"new_owner_email": "bobolive@example.com", "repo_name": "emmajohnson/image_transformation"}}

If only a username is required:
{"name": "git_transfer_repo_ownership", "parameters": {"new_owner_username": "bobolive", "repo_name": "emmajohnson/image_transformation"}}
